queries.query: INSERT INTO `api_accesslogs` (`vIPAddress`, `vAPIName`, `vAPIURL`, `dAccessDate`, `vPlatform`, `vBrowser`, `vFileName`) VALUES ('103.142.120.94', 'send_message', 'http://18.211.58.235/canoodle/WS/send_message', '2020-11-04 10:29:11', 'Unknown OS Platform', 'Unknown Browser', 'send_message-1604485751.json')

SELECT `uc`.`iUserId` AS `bu_blocked_to`,`uc`.`iConnectionUserId` AS `bu_blocked_by` FROM `user_connections` AS `uc` WHERE (uc.dtAddedAt IS NOT NULL AND uc.dtAddedAt <> '') AND ((uc.iUserId = 9 AND uc.iConnectionUserId = 6) OR (uc.iUserId = 6 AND uc.iConnectionUserId = 9)) AND `uc`.`eConnectionResult` = 'Block'  LIMIT 1

SELECT `m`.`iMessageId` AS `m_message_id` FROM `message` AS `m` WHERE `m`.`iMessageId` = 'xYmmMgsPYCYRwY6iZexf' OR (m.iSenderId IS NOT NULL AND m.iSenderId <> '') AND (m.iSenderId = 9 AND m.iReceiverId = 6) OR (m.iSenderId = 6 AND m.iReceiverId = 9)  LIMIT 1

SELECT `s`.`iUserId` AS `s_users_id`,`r`.`iUserId` AS `r_users_id`,`r`.`vDeviceToken` AS `r_device_token`,CONCAT(s.vFirstName," ",s.vLastName) AS s_name FROM `message` AS `m` LEFT JOIN `users` AS `s` ON `m`.`iSenderId` = `s`.`iUserId` LEFT JOIN `users` AS `r` ON `m`.`iReceiverId` = `r`.`iUserId` WHERE (m.iSenderId = 9 AND m.iReceiverId = 6)  LIMIT 1
SELECT `n`.`iNotificationId` AS `notification_id` FROM `notification` AS `n` WHERE `iUserId` IN('9') AND `vNotificationMessage` IN('Nick Jonas  has sent you a message.') AND `iNotifierId` IN('6')
UPDATE `notification` SET `dtUpdatedAt` = NOW() WHERE `iNotificationId` = '306' AND `eNotificationStatus` IN('Active')
SELECT `ui`.`vProfileImage` AS `ui_image`,`ui`.`iUserId` AS `ui_users_id` FROM `users` AS `ui` WHERE `ui`.`iUserId` = '9'  LIMIT 1
